      "settings": {
        "bg_video_url": "",
        "eyebrow": "The Founder",
        "title": "Why we started <em>MaxFoot.</em>",
        "body": "<p>In 2019, after watching too many friends and family members choose between overpriced premium trikes and unsafe budget options, we decided to build something different. Not another gadget for tech bros — a real, dependable electric tricycle that an American senior, a working parent, or a weekend rider could actually afford and actually trust.</p><p>Six years later, we're still building every model around the same four commitments: affordable pricing, dependable quality, real-world usability, and continuous improvement. If it doesn't ride well in a grocery store parking lot, it doesn't ship.</p>",
        "signature": "Coulson, Founder"
      }
    },
